<template>
  <v-card class="overflow-hidden">
    <v-app-bar
      absolute
      color="#6A76AB"
      dark
       prominent

      <template v-slot:img="{ props }">
        <v-img
          v-bind="props"
          gradient="to top right, rgba(100,115,201,.7), rgba(25,32,72,.7)"

      max-height="600"

    </v-sheet>
